headline: GEHC- A Healthcare Equipment Stock That Will Benefit from Trade Deals
summary: Stocks have rallied 30% from April’s Liberation Day low, when President Trump announced double-digit tariffs on global trading partners. Despite signs of progress, US exporters remain under pressure…and therein lies the opportunity. I like GE HealthCare Technologies Inc. (GEHC), advises Adam Johnson, editor of Bullseye Brief.
